      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a great project car or a reliable daily driver for someone who doesn't mind some cosmetic imperfections. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, some fading paint on the roof, and a few small dings. Inside, the upholstery has some visible wear and a small tear on the driver's seat. Mechanically, it runs and drives, though it may require some upcoming maintenance for items like brake pads and a suspension tune-up. It's an honest car that has been used regularly and is priced according to its current state.",
