      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You've honestly gotta see this beauty in person. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, and I\u2019ve kept it in such incredible shape that it still looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! Not a single scratch or dent to be found, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the dealership headache, this is the one. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I\u2019d love to see it go to a great home!",
      "price": 46500.0,
