    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, maintained to the highest possible standards and presenting in showroom condition. The exterior retains its deep, factory-original luster with zero swirl marks, chips, or dings, having been professionally ceramic coated and stored exclusively in a climate-controlled garage. Inside, the cabin remains pristine; the premium leather seats show no bolster wear, and every electronic component functions flawlessly. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach. I have a comprehensive binder containing every service record from day one, documenting all scheduled maintenance and preventative care performed using only genuine OEM parts. With exceptionally low mileage and a clean history, this car drives exactly as it did when it first rolled off the assembly line\u2014tight, responsive, and silent. This is a rare opportunity to own a museum-quality example that has been pampered by a meticulous enthusiast.",
      "price": 46500.0,
